.TH PRODBOX_aws 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-aws \- AWS IAM and quota management
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox aws
.SH DESCRIPTION
Operational AWS administration commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBpolicy\fR
Render IAM policy JSON
.TP
\fBsetup\fR
Create or refresh operational IAM user
.TP
\fBteardown\fR
Delete operational IAM user
.TP
\fBquotas\fR
Inspect or request AWS quotas
.TP
\fBebs\fR
AWS EBS maintenance
.TP
\fBstack\fR
AWS substrate stack lifecycle
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox aws policy\fR
Inspect the IAM policy without mutating AWS.
